    /////////////
    /// INTRO ///
    /////////////
    header#page-top.intro
      .intro-body
        .container
          video#intro-video(autoplay='autoplay', loop='loop', poster='volleyball.jpg')
            source(src='video/volleyball.mp4', type='video/mp4')
            source(src='video/volleyball.webm', type='video/webm')   
          .row
            .col-md-8.col-md-offset-2
              image.intro-logo(src="/img/SBSL-Logo.png")
              h2.intro-text
                | LA'S PREMIER SPORTS LEAGUE FOR STARTUPS
              p  
                a.btn.btn-default.btn-huge(href='mailto:hello@sbsportsleague.com?subject=Sign Me Up!') REGISTER    
          .row
            ul.nav.navbar-nav
              //
                 Hidden li included to remove active class from about link when scrolled up past about section 
              li.hidden
                a(href='#page-top')
              li.page-scroll
                a(href='#about') About
              li.page-scroll
                a(href='#feedback') Schedule                
              li.page-scroll
                a(href='#faq') FAQ
              li.page-scroll
                a(href='#contact') Contact 
  
    /////////////
    /// ABOUT ///
    /////////////    
    section#about.container
      .row
        .col-lg-8.col-lg-offset-2 
          h2.section-heading About   
          h4.section-subheading Silicon Beach Sports League         
          p The Silicon Beach Sports League provides an environment for company employees, investors, and other entrepreneurs in Los Angeles to build connections in a startup community committed to staying fit. The League organizes tournaments and scrimmages for multiple sports including soccer, volleyball, ultimate frisbee, basketball, golf, and dodgeball.

    ////////////////
    /// SCHEDULE ///
    ////////////////
    section#schedule.container
      .bg-overlay
      .row
        .col-lg-8.col-lg-offset-2
          h1.section-heading.white Week 1
          h3.section-subheading.white VOLLEYBALL TOURNAMENT
          p
            b.section-subheading August 24 | Hermosa Beach, CA
          p  
            a.btn.btn-default.btn-huge(href='mailto:hello@sbsportsleague.com?subject=Sign Me Up!') REGISTER
          br
          p
            b.section-subheading 8 Teams | 4 Players Per Team | $250 Entry Per Team
          p
            b.section-subheading All proceeds donated to
              a(href='http://villagecare.com' , target='_blank')  Village Care International
          a.villagecare-logo(href='http://villagecare.com')
            image(src='img/villagecare.png')

    ///////////
    /// FAQ ///
    ///////////
    section#faq.container(style='text-align:center')
        .row
          .col-lg-8.col-lg-offset-2
            h1.section-heading FAQ
            h4.section-subheading Frequently Asked Questions
            p 
              b Who can play?
              p Teams should consist of at least four players, and everyone on your company team should be either a founder, board member, employee, investor, or contractor.
            p
              b How does the tournament work? 
              p The tournament will have a double-elimination structure. There will be an entry fee of $250 per team - 100% of proceeds not used for the event are donated to the nonprofit organization 
                a(href='http://villagecare.com' , target='_blank') Village Care 
                |to support international humanitarian efforts. 
            p
              b What should I bring? 
              p Bring suntan lotion and your game face! Volleyballs will be provided! Please rep your company swag! Bring friends and family to come watch you play and enjoy the fun!
            p
              b Will refreshments be provided? 
              p Light snacks and water will be provided to keep you fueled for the game!              

    ////////////////
    /// PARTNERS ///
    ////////////////
      section#partners.container
          .row
            .col-lg-8.col-lg-offset-2
              h1.section-heading Partners
              .col-lg-4
                a(href='http://enplug.com')
                 .partner-logo(style='background-image: url(\'../img/enplug.png\')')
              .col-lg-4
                a(href)
                  

    ///////////////
    /// CONTACT ///
    ///////////////
    section#contact.container(style='text-align:center')
        .row
          .col-lg-8.col-lg-offset-2
            h1.section-heading Contact
            p Interested in joining? Reach out to us at 
              a(href='mailto:hello@sbsportsleague') hello@sbsportsleague.com!


   
